Version 1.1.0 (December XX 2016 for Haiku Nightly Image)
Mutilthreaded task queue for when multiple depots are changed
Created a status view in the corner of the depot list to replace the former task status progress window
Replaced system calls to pkgman with classes from the PackageKit
Created timers for each task to detect a possibly stuck task
User presented option to kill a stuck task
Bug fixes:
Web link cursor sometimes remained when About window closed


